  <blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="es" dir="ltr">4/05/2025 19h19min<br>📍Ayete, San Sebastián, Guipúzcoa, País Vasco<br>Ubicacíon actualizada <a href="https://t.co/0zK3cbCXhP">pic.twitter.com/0zK3cbCXhP</a></p>&mdash; Radar - 21 Días (@21diasradar) <a href="https://twitter.com/21diasradar/status/1919080609437093976?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">May 4, 2025</a></blockquote> <script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script>
